import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Bank } from '../bank/bank'; import { BankService } from '../service/bank.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-bank-list', templateUrl: '../bank-list/bank-list.component.html', styleUrls: ['./bank-list.component.css'] }) export class BankListComponent implements OnInit { banks: Bank[] | undefined; constructor(private bankService: BankService) { } ngOnInit() { this.bankService.findAll().subscribe((data: Bank[] | undefined) => { this.banks = data; }); } }
